data.description: Back On Market. No fault of the Home. Nestled in the sought-after community of Coppell, this home is conveniently located near top-rated schools, parks, and shopping centers. Enjoy the perks of a quiet neighborhood while still having easy access to major highways for a seamless commute. This single-story gem in Coppell, presents a rare opportunity to own a residence that balances elegance and practicality. Don't miss the chance to make this house your forever home! Schedule your showing today!
